[DhtmlXQ_comment34]An important move, removing the final roadblock. This horse needs to move back to the throat rank of his side of the board now, to free the chariot for the final kill.[/DhtmlXQ_comment34]
[DhtmlXQ_comment45]An extra piece is added to the black's cannon line of fire, freeing the chariot for the checkmate.[/DhtmlXQ_comment45]
